ygData.messageBody:
The guild can be found underneath the arena in
Qeynos. You go down there and will see some warriors down
there... if you look carefull you will see bones on the
ground making a kind of path it will lead you to a
secret passage through a wall. The scret passage is in
the one of the "cells" bring a lightsource though
because it is verry dark down there. Then you'll zone
into the sewers system of Qeynos don't take the first
left but go straight on you will allready see some
Shadow Knight and Necro NPC here at the end on the right
is a gate where all the evil guilds are.<br><br>Be
carefull in Qeynos though, there are people in the town
that will kill you on sight. I was killed by a monk
NPC and by a Half Elf at the docks...
